| Feature             | Sequelize              | TypeORM                       |
| ------------------- | ---------------------- | ----------------------------- |
| Language            | JS / TS                | TypeScript (best)             |
| Model style         | JS classes or define() | Decorators (@Entity, @Column) |
| Easy for beginners  | Yes                    | Moderate                      |
| Supports migrations | Yes                    | Yes                           |
| NestJS support      | Medium                 | Excellent                     |
| Learning curve      | Easy                   | Medium                        |
| Query builder       | Medium                 | Strong                        |
